description: Dallas singer 4batz rose from obscurity to a breathlessly awaited debut in barely a year — but his arrival is part of a tense exchange between hip-hop and R&B more than a decade in the making.
title: A new face, and new chapter, in R&B's unstoppable rap makeover

description: El Niño helped drive global average temperatures to new records over the last year. Forecasters say it's waning, but that 2024 may still be one for the record books.
title: El Niño is on the way out after a record-breaking year of heat
